{"tid":1860520,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［多謝手足］事實證明工會係幾重要","createTime":"2020-02-03T16:43:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T11:55:48.000Z","uid":335921,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5e09de70e636cf2b3ecbffbf2f64619ac9022c61","tid":1860520,"uid":335921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T16:43:17.000Z","msg":"三罷三罷 罷咗大半年都冇次做得成<br />\n一日到黑好嬲好嬲 然後繼續由得班後生仔去死<br />\n依家有個機會比你地補鑊啦一眾打工仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次罷得成真係工會嘅功勞<br />\n唔單止罷得成仲令到唔少界別吹起罷工<br />\n<br />\n可能你會話依家先罷得一兩日 有幾大分別姐<br />\n<br />\n但要知道由零碎幾丁友罷咗冇人知 <br />\n到二千人齊罷工全香港知<br />\n係個好大嘅鼓舞黎<br />\n<br />\n幾多唔敢罷嘅因為見到依二千人而加入<br />\n幾多唔知乜野叫罷工嘅港豬上咗一堂<br />\n<br />\n要再強調 二千人罷工可能好少 <br />\n但絕對係為香港工運行出咗月球上嘅第一步<br />\n<br />\n希望醫護手足撐住 未罷嘅快啲去罷<br />\n一日唔跪唔好返工<br />\n就算我中肺炎都唔想係醫院見到你地班靚仔靚女<br />\n<br />\n其他行業都要盡快動員加入<br />\n未入工會嘅小心比我錫春袋<br />\n快啲入工會啦 係咪要我手把手教你登記<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n來吧香港人<br />\n罷啦罷罷罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f077032917d54052c6ca407765c0595aa8b205c","tid":1860520,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T16:44:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5a4047f84ba0504ec9933ce80bcc406b596312","tid":1860520,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T16:44:22.000Z","msg":"大家入左各自公會未"},{"pid":"f34e14c2c8a6818031f321ecee0a3a95b3b8f01c","tid":1860520,"uid":321803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e09de70e636cf2b3ecbffbf2f64619ac9022c61","tid":1860520,"uid":335921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20